item.title: Tailor Made - Scarlit Scandal, Kenzie Anne, Troy Francisco
item.description: Scarlit takes on a mysterious job as a tailor on the top floor of an old mansion. Every night, partygoers wear the elaborate costumes that she and the resident tailor, Kenzie, design. Kenzie has gone this long without asking any questions, but Scarlit's curiosity drags them both into whatever is going on behind the doors.

item.title: Drift EP 5 - Maitland Ward, Mick Blue, Seth Gamble
item.description: Maitland connects again with the costar with whom she's played this evening's game. As she runs a straight-edged razor across his throat to make herself a smoother seat, Seth introduces his offering. He says, "I know bodies won't impress you, but you've always been a sucker for context," and with that delivers to Maitland what he knew she'd been holding out for: a DP with the two men she's only ever allowed to play coy with on screen. The pair return to the set of their sitcom, where Mick waits patiently. Maitland pulls him up by the throat and sizes him up as she snarls, "Make it count". Part 5 of 5

item.title: Drift EP 4 - Maitland Ward, Danny Mountain
item.description: Still looking to cram in another hit before she comes to Seth again, Maitland snatches an easy target in the form of a wheelchair-bound man left waiting outside. Part 4 of 5

item.title: Drift EP 3 - Little Dragon, Jamie Knoxx, Coach Cardher, Maitland Ward
item.description: Little Dragon reminds Maitland of her former self: a young redhead feigning modesty while all the signs of a much richer life are hiding in plain sight. Scaring her into not losing any more time, Maitland creates a new game. She raises the stakes so that this younger woman is either forced to lie and forgo a life-changing sum of cash or admit something about herself in order to keep the riches. Part 3 of 5

item.title: Drift EP 2 - Maitland Ward, Alex Jones
item.description: At a premiere the same night, one of Maitland's costars invites her to come home with him. Her response is that she'll only come to him if he can present her with something better than what she might find herself, and so sets off adrift through a seedy urban nightscape in this game they've created. Maitland's next mark is easy. He's already watching her. Part 2 of 5

item.title: Make It Happen - Mona Azar, Alyx Star, Michael Vegas, Milan
item.description: A conservative Sunday brunch between two successful couples takes a left turn when Mona pushes Alyx's husband, Michael, to find a way for them to hook up. Under pressure, he finds a way to disguise their relationship behind an impromptu game of wife swapping.
